<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.7">
<l>uṟṟārka ḷeṉakkillai yāru meṉṉu muṟṟārka ḷeṉakkiṅkel lāru meṉṉu</l>
<l>muṟṟārkaḷaic ceyvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu muṟṟārkaḷai yaḻippēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>muṟṟārkaḷuk kuṟṟēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉu muṟṟārili māyaṉ vantēṟak kolō</l>
<l>vuṟṟīrkaṭ keṉcollic collu kēṉyā ṉuṟṟeṉ ṉuṭaippē taiyuraik kiṉṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I have nobody who experiences [me]”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I have everyone here that experiences [me]”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who makes those who experience [me]”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who cares for those who experience [me]”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who experiences for those who experience [me]”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the Dark one without those who experience [him] settles in [her]?</l>
<l>What will I say, speaking to you who have experience,</l>
	<l>[words] that talk to the foolish [daughter] I have?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
